snippet.title: Fishermurs trailer
snippet.description:
Fishermurs - the game about paddles, lemurs and fish! 
The problem is that 4 lemurs have only 1 fish.. And they need to fight for it! 
All aboard! Grab your paddle, hop in a boat, and beat up anyone who tries to snatch your precious fish. 
Now on Steam EarlyAccess!
